extends layoutBS

block content
  .margin
    .margin3
      h2 Trip Planner
      .margin2
        h4.text-center Start a new trip
        br
        form(method="post")
          .form-row
            .form-group.col-md-6
              label(for="destination") Destination
              input#destination.form-control(name="country" type="text" placeholder="Country")
            .form-group.col-md-6
              label(for="city") City 
              input#city.form-control(name="city" type="text" placeholder="City")
          .form-row
            .form-group.col-md-6
              label(for="departDate") Departure Date
              input#departDate.form-control(name="depdate" type="date" placeholder="06.10.2018")
            .form-group.col-md-6
              label(for="returnDate") Return Date
              input#returnDate.form-control(name="retdate" type="date" placeholder="06.10.2018")
          .form-group
            label(for="hotel") Hotel
            select#hotel(name="hotel").form-control
              option(selected="") Choose...
              option Hilton
              option Sheraton
              option Westin
              option Four Seasons
              option Ritz-Carlton
              option Hyatt
              option Renaissance
              option Embassy Suites
              option InterContinental
              option JetBlue
              option Hyatt Regency
              option Shangri-La
              option Wyndham
              option Grant Hyatt
              option Fairmont
              option JW Marriot
              option Sofitel
              option Loews
              option Mandarin Oriental
              option Conrad
              option Peninsula
          .form-group
            label(for="airline") Airline
            select#airline(name="airline").form-control
              option(selected="") Choose...
              option Asiana Airline
              option Air New Zealand
              option Air France
              option Austrian Airlines
              option All Nippon Airlines
              option Cathay Pacific Airways
              option Delta Air Lines
              option Etihad Airways
              option EVA Air
              option JetBlue
              option Hainan Airline
              option Lufthansa
              option Japan Airlines
              option Qantas Airline
              option Qatar Airways
              option Singapore Airlines
              option Swiss International Air Lines
              option United Airlines
              option Thai Airways
              option Turkish Airlines
              option Virgin Australia
          .form-group
            label(for="purpose") Travel purpose
            input#purpose.form-control(name="purpose" type="text")
          button.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg(type="submit") Go
      br
      br
      br
      br
      br
      p
        | The destination is #{city}, #{country}.

      br
      p.font-weight-bold Best Hotels
        .row
          .col-4
            #list-tab.list-group(role="tablist")
              a#list-home-list.list-group-item.list-group-item-action.active(data-toggle="list" href="#list-1" role="tab" aria-controls="home") Nihi Sumba Island, Indonesia
              a#list-profile-list.list-group-item.list-group-item-action(data-toggle="list" href="#list-2" role="tab" aria-controls="profile") The Brando, Tetiatoa, French Polynesia
              a#list-messages-list.list-group-item.list-group-item-action(data-toggle="list" href="#list-3" role="tab" aria-controls="messages") Lodge&Spa at Brush Creek Ranch, Saratoga, Wyoming
              a#list-settings-list.list-group-item.list-group-item-action(data-toggle="list" href="#list-4" role="tab" aria-controls="settings") Lodge at Kauri Cliffs, Matauri Bay, New Zealand
              a#list-settings-list.list-group-item.list-group-item-action(data-toggle="list" href="#list-5" role="tab" aria-controls="settings") Gibb's Farm, Karatu, Tanzania
              a#list-settings-list.list-group-item.list-group-item-action(data-toggle="list" href="#list-5" role="tab" aria-controls="settings") More
          .col-8
            #nav-tabContent.tab-content
              #list-1.tab-pane.fade.show.active(role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="list-home-list")
                |A cluster of rustic-luxe villas perched above a stretch of unspoilt Sumbanese coast, Nihi Sumba hotel feels perched on the edge of the world.
                |Preserved from urban development, this off-the-beaten-path Indonesian island is an idyllic setting for once-in-a-lifetime romance.
                br
                br
                img.card-img-topimg(src='/images/nihi.jpg' width='60%')
              #list-2.tab-pane.fade(role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="list-profile-list")
                |The Brando is a unique luxury resort on French Polynesia’s breathtakingly beautiful private island of Tetiaroa – an atoll composed of a dozen small islands surrounding a sparkling lagoon 30 miles northeast of Tahiti.
                br
                br
                img.card-img-topimg(src='/images/brando.jpg' width='60%')
              #list-3.tab-pane.fade(role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="list-messages-list")
                |The Lodge & Spa at Brush Creek Ranch, a luxury boutique guest ranch in Saratoga, Wyoming, is the perfect place to unwind and experience life on true working ranch in the Great American West.
                |From log-hewn buildings to stone fireplaces to plenty of outdoor activities, this Saratoga guest ranch makes every guest feel at home on 30,000 private acres.
                br
                br
                img.card-img-topimg(src='/images/lodgebrush.png' width='50%')
              #list-4.tab-pane.fade(role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="list-settings-list")
                |With sweeping views of the Pacific Ocean, The Lodge at Kauri Cliffs hotel on the North Island of New Zealand entices at every turn.
                |A four hour drive from Auckland, this hideaway is set in the middle of 6,000 acres near Matauri Bay – overlooking Cape Brett and the Cavalli Islands.
                br
                br
                img.card-img-topimg(src='/images/kauricliff.jpg' width='50%')
              #list-5.tab-pane.fade(role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="list-settings-list")
                |Gibbs farm is not just a stop off point for the Ngorongoro Crater and other nearby safari delights.  It’s a hotel that offers peace, tranquillity and a return to a different way of life!
                |The guests are actively encouraged to become at one with their surroundings and emerge themselves into the ‘rhythm of the farm’.
                br
                br
                img.card-img-topimg(src='/images/gibbsfarm.jpg' width='50%')

        br
        br
        p.font-weight-bold Best Airlines
          .row
            .col-4
              #list-tab.list-group(role="tablist")
                a#list-home-list.list-group-item.list-group-item-action.active(data-toggle="list" href="#list2-1" role="tab" aria-controls="home") Qatar Airways
                a#list-profile-list.list-group-item.list-group-item-action(data-toggle="list" href="#list2-2" role="tab" aria-controls="profile") Lufthansa
                a#list-messages-list.list-group-item.list-group-item-action(data-toggle="list" href="#list2-3" role="tab" aria-controls="messages") Etihad Airways
                a#list-settings-list.list-group-item.list-group-item-action(data-toggle="list" href="#list2-4" role="tab" aria-controls="settings") Singapore Airlines
                a#list-settings-list.list-group-item.list-group-item-action(data-toggle="list" href="#list2-5" role="tab" aria-controls="settings") South African Airways
                a#list-settings-list.list-group-item.list-group-item-action(data-toggle="list" href="#list2-5" role="tab" aria-controls="settings") More
            .col-8
              #nav-tabContent.tab-content
                #list2-1.tab-pane.fade.show.active(role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="list-home-list")
                  | The best airline in the world, according to the AirHelp Score, is Qatar Airways, which landed a perfect 10 for quality of service, an 8.86 claim processing score, and an 89% on-time performance score.
                  br
                  br
                  img.card-img-topimg(src='/images/qatar.jpg' width='70%')
                #list2-2.tab-pane.fade(role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="list-profile-list")
                  |The German airline came in second place thanks to its score of 10 for service and 8.63 for claim processing, beat out only due to it 76% punctuality score.
                  br
                  br
                  img.card-img-topimg(src='/images/lufthansa.jpg' width='70%')
                #list2-3.tab-pane.fade(role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="list-messages-list")
                  |The UAE's Etihad is constantly named among the best airlines in the world, and with a score of 9 on service, 86% for punctuality, and 7.47 for claim processing, it's easy to see why.
                  br
                  br
                  img.card-img-topimg(src='/images/etihad.jpg' width='60%')
                #list2-4.tab-pane.fade(role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="list-settings-list")
                  |Set to launch the longest flight in the world at 19 hours from Singapore to New York, it's lucky Singapore's airline offers a full 10/10 for quality of service, as well as 85% on-time performance. Only its claim processing score — 6.77 — brought it down to fourth place this year.
                  br
                  br
                  img.card-img-topimg(src='/images/singapore.jpg' width='70%')
                #list2-5.tab-pane.fade(role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="list-settings-list")
                  | The 8.69 claim processing score, 8 on service, and 85% on-time performance put South Africa's airline in fifth place.
                  br
                  br
                  img.card-img-topimg(src='/images/southafrica.jpg' width='70%')

        br
        br
        br
        br
        p.font-weight-bold Top Reviews
